    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "On the related pull-request #155, @substack proposed a [solution](https://github.com/substack/node-browserify/pull/155#issuecomment-5958779) based on an option flag that appears to be a good compromise for this issue.\n\nSo, unless there is something really problematic with that, I think i'll try an implementation of this sometime..\n\nAnyway, a standalone buffer module would be appreciated by everyone. @toots , do you plan to extract your implementation of _buffer_ in a standalone module one day please ? \n",
